verses.text_plain: May mercy, peace, and love be multiplied to you.

verses.text_plain: Beloved, although I was very eager to write to you about our common salvation, I found it necessary to write appealing to you to contend for the faith that was once for all delivered to the saints.

verses.text_plain: For certain people have crept in unnoticed who long ago were designated for this condemnation, ungodly people, who pervert the grace of our God into sensuality and deny our only Master and Lord, Jesus Christ.

verses.text_plain: Yet in like manner these people also, relying on their dreams, defile the flesh, reject authority, and blaspheme the glorious ones.
verses.verse_html: 8Yet in like manner these people also, relying on their dreams, defile the flesh, reject authority, and xblaspheme the glorious ones.

verses.text_plain: But when the archangel Michael, contending with the devil, was disputing about the body of Moses, he did not presume to pronounce a blasphemous judgment, but said, “The Lord rebuke you.”
verses.verse_html: 9But when ythe archangel zMichael, contending with the devil, was disputing aaabout the body of Moses, he did not presume to pronounce a blasphemous judgment, but said, ab“The Lord rebuke you.”

verses.text_plain: But these people blaspheme all that they do not understand, and they are destroyed by all that they, like unreasoning animals, understand instinctively.
verses.verse_html: 10 acBut these people blaspheme all that they do not understand, and they are destroyed by all that they, like unreasoning animals, understand instinctively.

verses.text_plain: Woe to them! For they walked in the way of Cain and abandoned themselves for the sake of gain to Balaam’s error and perished in Korah’s rebellion.
